+PUT /v1/nfvs/{client_id}/forward
+~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
+
+Start or Stop forwarding.
+
+* Normal response codes: 204
+* Error response codes: 400, 404
+
+Request(path)
+^^^^^^^^^^^^^
+
+.. _table_spp_ctl_spp_nfv_forward_get:
