+    +===========+=========+=================================+
+    | client_id | integer | client id.                      |
+    +-----------+---------+---------------------------------+
+
+Request example
+^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
+
+.. code-block:: console
+
+    curl -X PUT -H 'application/json' \
+    -d '{"action": "start"}' \
+    http://127.0.0.1:7777/v1/nfvs/1/forward
+
+Request(body)
+^^^^^^^^^^^^^
+
+.. _table_spp_ctl_spp_nfv_forward_get_body:
+
+.. table:: Request body params of forward of spp_nfv or spp_vm.
+
+    +--------+--------+-------------------------------------+
